                     <interp inst="t17291203-9-person83" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , that they look'd at them, but let them alone, and first they fill'd a Basket, next a Bag, but before they had completed that, they rushed out upon them, and took the Prisoner, but his Brother ran away.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17291203-9-person84">
                  Thomas 
                  Nightingale 
               <interp inst="t17291203-9-person84" type="surname" value="Nightingale"></interp>
